%h1 Welcome to IDEALS
%p IDEALS, the Illinois Digital Environment for Access to Learning and Scholarship, publishes research and scholarship from the University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign.
%ul
  %li
    Faculty, staff, and graduate students can deposit their research and scholarship&mdash;unpublished and, in many cases, published&mdash;directly into IDEALS.
  %li
    Departments can use IDEALS to distribute their working papers, technical reports, or other research material.
  %li
    IDEALS also includes all electronic theses and dissertations deposited from Fall 2010 onward.
